history.content:
Hi David,

We connected over email, but I still wanted respond to your post.

This was not an error. It is typical for discussion and lab sections to have more spaces than the lecture to allow more options for students. Also, due to TA restraints, we had to decrease the size of the class. Since your post, students have dropped and there are currently a few open seats.

There is also an evening section available that still has open seats.

Hi, Babek Ayazifar's section for EE20 is listed as full (160 students) but there are still a many spots open in the discussion and lab sections. For example, the lab section 109 still has 15 spots open. I'm on the waitlist and I'm wondering if there has been an error? 

(I was originally reserved a spot for lecture 2 for EE20 but I'm switching sections.)
